  "title": "Nurse Educator (Office hours) #HJO",
  "description": "<h3>Key Responsibilities:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, develop, and deliver clinical training programs, workshops, and orientation for nurses across various departments.</li>\n  <li>Provide coaching and mentorship to new and junior nursing staff to ensure quality clinical practice and patient safety.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with Nursing Leaders and Department Heads to identify learning needs and support continuous professional development.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate competency assessments and skills evaluation to uphold nursing standards.</li>\n  <li>Participate in nursing research, quality improvement initiatives, and evidence-based practice implementation.</li>\n  <li>Stay current with MOH regulations, nursing practices, and emerging healthcare trends.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🔹 Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Registered Nurse</strong> with valid registration under the <strong>Singapore Nursing Board (SNB)</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree in Nursing or equivalent (Postgraduate qualifications in Nursing Education or Clinical Teaching preferred).</li>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>5 years of clinical experience</strong>, including experience in teaching, preceptorship, or staff development.</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal, communication, and presentation skills.</li>\n  <li>Passionate about lifelong learning, patient care, and staff empowerment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p>We regret only suitable candidates will be shortlisted for an interview.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
